responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "6BDD42164383AA4D8F05678992F8DDA7", "As expected, nothing but an ancient myth. While ancient indeed, this battleaxe courses with no essence.It\'s ancient edges have turned blunt and chipped. Leaving us with nothing more than scrap. Nay! I cannot return this to the Striders Vigilant. Let it be your reward. Perhaps it can even buy you a drink or two at the Green Scarab. Our work here is done.")
